skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: breeze sounds
des: Woosh! Let the calming sound of a smooth breeze lull you right to sleep. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Breeze Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
